A Birmingham band with their beginnings in 1974, Quartz signed to Jet in 1976 under the name of
Bandy Legs
.
Hopkins
played in
The Idle Race
with Jeff Lynne (also in The Move, E.L.O., etc.) in the early 1970s. Hopkins and bassist
Arnold
had also previously played together in
Copperfield
.

Reformed at the end of 2011.
